org.phantomapi.clust

Interface AsyncMultiDataHandler<T,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the Configurable object
    V - the bound object used to get the data
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AsyncDataController

    public interface AsyncMultiDataHandler<T,V>
    An interface for handing multiple data clustered objects with the same relative type. A Great example would be using this for playerdata
    Author:
    cyberpwn

      • isLoading

        boolean isLoading(V identifier)
        Checks if the config from the identifier is still loading on another thread
        Parameters:
        identifier - the identifier
        Returns:
        Returns true if the thread is still loading the config. Returns false if the config is finished loading, or was never loading in the first place.
